&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Title: Project Coordinator, Bond &amp;amp; Permit Release&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Type: &lt;/strong&gt;Full time, exempt (salary)&lt;/p&gt;
