&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Responsibilities:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Site visits to document the project status.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Meetings with County personnel.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Manage and communicate with utility companies.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Observe construction activities in the field.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&amp;nbsp;Prepare and deliver bond documents to County and State jurisdictions.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&amp;nbsp;Utilize computer software to organize project documents.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&amp;nbsp;Generate digital copy of punch lists and associated plans to send to clients.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&amp;nbsp;Support Bond Management Director and Senior Project Managers.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Review construction plans and plats.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
