&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Qualifications: &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;At a minimum 2 years of experience in construction, homebuilding or real estate development industries&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong professional communicator and organizational skills&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Permit applicaton and processing knowledge is preferred.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience using office technology suite; Word, Excel, Outlook, Teams, etc.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong communication and critical thinking skills&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience with reading construction plans&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Compensation:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Competitive Salary&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Yearly Bonus&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Health, Vision and Dental Insurance&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;PTO and Paid Holidays&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;401K w/ Company Match&lt;/li&gt;
